sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant F as Frontend
  participant B as Backend
  participant C as Coordinator
  participant A as Agents
  participant L as Ollama
  U->>F: Upload repo
  F->>B: POST /projects
  B-->>F: project_id
  F->>B: POST /analyses
  B-->>F: analysis_id (queued)
  B->>C: plan & dispatch
  C->>A: run(code_review)
  A->>L: prompt
  L-->>A: response
  A-->>C: findings
  C->>A: run(security)
  A->>L: prompt
  L-->>A: response
  A-->>C: findings
  C-->>B: merged
  B-->>F: status=completed
  F->>B: GET /reports/{id}/bundle
  B-->>F: zip
